room_title: Escape room "Serial Killer" by Break Out Myrtle Beach in Myrtle Beach
room_address: 314 Main St North Myrtle Beach, SC 29582
room_description: A cruel serial killer has trapped you and your friends in his house to play his unusual games of torture and despair. Now he is testing your basic knowledge to see if you are smart enough to escape the rooms of doom that he has created. You and your teammates have to use logic, problem-solving skills and creativity to survive, but you've got only 60 minutes. Soon you will realize that time is your worst enemy...
